OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSamsung appoints convicted 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fheir to top job            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, South Korean electronics giant Samsung 
OL,6, has named convicted heir and de facto  
OL,7, boss Lee Jae-yong as its executive     
OL,8, chairman.                              
OL,10,FThe symbolic move means the world's    
OL,11,Fbiggest smartphone maker will now be   
OL,12,Fofficially run by the third generation 
OL,13,Fof its founding family.                
OL,15,FMr Lee, who was convicted of bribery   
OL,16,Fand embezzlement in 2017, was granted a
OL,17,Fspecial presidential pardon in August. 
OL,19,FHe was imprisoned twice for bribing a  
OL,20,Fformer president.                      
